WEBVTT

01:31.700 --> 01:35.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:35.980 --> 01:38.980
[Episode 14]

02:20.240 --> 02:21.410
What a pity.

02:24.150 --> 02:25.680
We were this close to finding the answer.

02:29.590 --> 02:30.660
The prayer ceremony

02:31.030 --> 02:32.130
begins now.

02:35.120 --> 02:36.220
Isn't the prayer ceremony

02:36.240 --> 02:37.930
supposed to be held two days before the wedding?

02:38.590 --> 02:39.220
Besides,

02:40.560 --> 02:42.340
I've already stolen the Radiant Moon.

02:44.120 --> 02:45.170
What's going on?

02:47.430 --> 02:48.570
People always say

02:49.560 --> 02:50.570
that the past can't be changed,

02:51.280 --> 02:52.410
and that years flow like water.

02:53.630 --> 02:54.730
This is the first time

02:55.080 --> 02:56.820
I've felt it so vividly.

02:57.800 --> 02:58.540
Humans

02:59.190 --> 03:00.130
and demons alike,

03:00.870 --> 03:02.220
even the Dragon Deity himself,

03:02.870 --> 03:04.120
are so small

03:04.910 --> 03:06.420
before fate.

03:07.190 --> 03:08.260
Inside the Star Stone

03:09.280 --> 03:10.630
is an illusion of the past.

03:11.190 --> 03:12.520
Since it's the past,

03:12.910 --> 03:14.340
it cannot be reversed

03:14.710 --> 03:15.340
or changed.

03:16.090 --> 03:16.820
The moment

03:16.840 --> 03:18.480
something that could alter the past happens,

03:19.430 --> 03:21.220
the illusion will shift and leap,

03:22.030 --> 03:22.820
correcting itself automatically

03:23.310 --> 03:24.610
to erase the traces of error

03:26.560 --> 03:27.690
and move on to the next

03:28.590 --> 03:30.340
destined moment that cannot be changed.

03:48.820 --> 03:50.730
You keep looking at me without saying anything.

03:51.520 --> 03:52.480
What do you want?

03:54.840 --> 03:55.690
If you'd known

03:56.750 --> 03:58.220
you couldn't use demon magic just now,

04:02.240 --> 04:03.220
would you still have stepped

04:03.240 --> 04:04.380
in front of me without hesitation?

04:08.310 --> 04:09.380
Of course not.

04:09.800 --> 04:10.540
I'm not stupid.

04:36.870 --> 04:37.730
What are you looking at?

04:39.740 --> 04:40.430
The moon.

04:44.600 --> 04:45.140
Don't be ridiculous.

04:46.430 --> 04:47.810
The sky is pitch-black.

04:48.120 --> 04:48.730
Where's the moon?

04:50.070 --> 04:50.540
It's there.

04:52.310 --> 04:53.250
It's called Hui.
[*new moon]

04:59.040 --> 04:59.780
I've heard

05:00.480 --> 05:02.090
that everyone in the Formless Moon

05:02.160 --> 05:03.660
has a mark on their arm.

05:04.390 --> 05:05.340
Why don't you have one?

05:07.430 --> 05:10.410
Because my moon phase is Hui.

05:11.600 --> 05:12.050
Hui?

05:12.630 --> 05:13.270
When you

05:13.270 --> 05:14.850
can't see the moon at night,

05:15.510 --> 05:16.490
that moon phase

05:17.600 --> 05:18.250
is Hui.

05:20.480 --> 05:21.370
You said

05:22.360 --> 05:23.950
that even if you were shattered to pieces,

05:24.160 --> 05:25.150
you could still be reborn.

05:26.430 --> 05:27.620
But will the reborn you

05:29.800 --> 05:30.890
still be the original you?

05:33.240 --> 05:35.170
The Primordial Sacred Spring can share

05:35.750 --> 05:36.810
and preserve memories.

05:37.630 --> 05:39.410
We are all reborn with memories.

05:39.850 --> 05:41.010
That's incredible.

05:43.190 --> 05:44.580
What does it feel like

05:46.120 --> 05:47.290
to share memories with others?

05:50.800 --> 05:52.250
It's hard to explain.

05:54.190 --> 05:54.900
Is it really?

05:59.160 --> 06:00.700
The Golden Scale Tree in the Shilin Sect

06:00.750 --> 06:02.470
has always had a special fragrance.

06:02.630 --> 06:03.350
You know that, right?

06:03.920 --> 06:04.340
Of course.

06:05.750 --> 06:06.660
Then how would you

06:06.680 --> 06:08.130
describe that scent to someone

06:08.190 --> 06:09.580
who's never been to the Shilin Sect?

06:14.750 --> 06:15.590
I think

06:17.630 --> 06:18.580
I understand what you mean now.

06:20.120 --> 06:21.140
Take

06:22.360 --> 06:23.650
the special scent you carry

06:23.650 --> 06:24.910
for example.

06:25.240 --> 06:26.530
I can't describe what it's like either.

06:27.390 --> 06:28.910
You've described it plenty of times,

06:29.950 --> 06:30.770
comparing it

06:31.630 --> 06:32.730
to wildflowers in a mountain valley

06:33.310 --> 06:34.170
and heavy snow at an ancient temple.

06:37.680 --> 06:38.930
Do I really carry a scent?

06:40.920 --> 06:41.730
You do.

06:42.270 --> 06:43.410
You always think I'm lying to you.

06:47.160 --> 06:48.660
Maybe it's just my natural scent.

06:57.180 --> 06:58.740
There's no new moon in the sky,

06:59.790 --> 07:01.230
just like I didn't exist in the Formless Moon either

07:02.600 --> 07:03.210
at the very start.

07:04.870 --> 07:06.300
When I was first born,

07:07.710 --> 07:08.860
I always dreamed

07:10.320 --> 07:11.090
that my sisters

07:11.160 --> 07:12.740
couldn't see me

07:13.630 --> 07:15.220
when I was with them.

07:18.580 --> 07:20.740
♪In the light, the great tree♪

07:21.100 --> 07:26.260
♪Sways gently, watching the mortal world burn bright♪

07:26.740 --> 07:28.140
♪Oh, little blade of grass♪

07:28.620 --> 07:32.940
♪I want to go somewhere else♪

07:33.860 --> 07:36.660
♪How do you measure memory♪

07:36.900 --> 07:41.740
♪To cut the past into clothes to wear?♪

07:41.860 --> 07:44.780
♪The little blade of grass, eyes brimming with tears♪

07:44.900 --> 07:49.540
♪Holds fallen leaves and grieves♪

07:50.620 --> 07:52.780
♪Summer heat fades into autumn's chill♪

07:52.860 --> 07:54.540
♪Winter snow falls in haste♪

07:54.660 --> 07:58.260
♪Then spring dew brings hope again♪

07:58.900 --> 08:00.100
♪Don't be afraid♪

08:00.540 --> 08:03.820
♪The passing years are nothing more than an evening glow♪

08:05.160 --> 08:05.780
Wangyan,

08:07.000 --> 08:07.850
thank you.

08:11.360 --> 08:12.810
You're the only one who can see me.

08:13.720 --> 08:15.540
You always hide in the dark.

08:16.360 --> 08:17.100
Of course the others

08:17.100 --> 08:18.450
can't see you easily.

08:20.440 --> 08:21.370
But I can.

08:22.720 --> 08:23.460
My heart

08:24.920 --> 08:26.490
can feel where you are.

08:28.600 --> 08:29.220
Later,

08:29.870 --> 08:31.800
Wangyan always took me with her wherever she went.

08:32.730 --> 08:33.940
And I never had

08:33.940 --> 08:35.240
those lonely dreams again.

08:36.790 --> 08:38.250
Though the new moon exists,

08:39.200 --> 08:40.650
barely anyone can see it.

08:43.630 --> 08:44.890
Only those who care about it

08:45.790 --> 08:47.010
will keep looking up

08:48.910 --> 08:50.770
and search for it in all that darkness.

08:54.840 --> 08:55.730
I can see it.

08:58.630 --> 09:00.370
Whether it's the waxing and waning moon

09:01.720 --> 09:02.980
or the stars spread across the sky,

09:04.550 --> 09:05.770
they all have their own orbits.

09:07.740 --> 09:08.720
No place

09:10.080 --> 09:10.980
can ever replace another.

09:17.200 --> 09:18.130
You're the Dragon Deity.

09:18.840 --> 09:19.770
Of course you wouldn't understand.

09:21.670 --> 09:22.890
But even the Dragon Deity will fall.

09:23.720 --> 09:25.010
My eight elder brothers

09:26.030 --> 09:26.890
are all gone.

09:28.750 --> 09:29.370
And one day,

09:30.720 --> 09:31.490
I will

09:33.600 --> 09:35.130
step down from this divine throne too.

09:38.840 --> 09:39.850
Are you afraid

09:41.750 --> 09:43.010
of falling,

09:44.790 --> 09:45.820
of no longer being a deity

09:45.840 --> 09:47.180
revered by all?

10:18.720 --> 10:19.340
Who would've thought?

10:21.240 --> 10:22.370
The stone we've been searching for

10:23.790 --> 10:24.580
is actually a person.

10:29.030 --> 10:30.210
But didn't the Star Stone

10:30.210 --> 10:32.270
shatter in that Meteor Blast long ago?

10:34.720 --> 10:35.680
Master Chi Wen,

10:37.320 --> 10:38.720
the Dragon Deity, saved me.

10:47.440 --> 10:49.060
I am disaster itself.

10:50.600 --> 10:51.820
I am the abyss.

10:54.030 --> 10:55.580
Why did you save me?

10:56.840 --> 10:58.420
If all it takes is one pebble falling

10:59.030 --> 10:59.980
to break the silence,

11:01.620 --> 11:03.340
then it is no longer an abyss.

11:05.270 --> 11:07.340
You bear extraordinary power from beyond the heavens.

11:07.790 --> 11:08.340
Slaughter

11:08.870 --> 11:10.420
is not your only choice.

11:12.000 --> 11:13.420
Now that your chains are gone,

11:13.870 --> 11:14.530
you are free.

11:15.270 --> 11:16.580
So is your will.

11:17.320 --> 11:18.100
It is up to you

11:18.630 --> 11:19.530
to choose

11:20.480 --> 11:21.610
between slaughter and protection.

11:23.320 --> 11:24.610
I hope that one day,

11:24.870 --> 11:27.290
you'll find the true meaning of coming to this world

11:27.600 --> 11:28.970
after crossing

11:29.270 --> 11:30.340
countless galaxies.

11:31.510 --> 11:33.300
Master Chi Wen even gave me a dragon fang

11:34.510 --> 11:36.060
and taught me how to control my power.

11:37.270 --> 11:38.850
But in the end, countless lives

11:38.870 --> 11:39.770
were still lost because of me.

11:40.600 --> 11:41.580
I couldn't forgive myself.

11:42.630 --> 11:43.580
After that,

11:43.960 --> 11:44.980
I became a monk

11:45.630 --> 11:46.530
and shaved my head.

11:47.340 --> 11:49.800
From that day on, there was no more Star Stone and no more Tian Di.

11:50.550 --> 11:52.190
Later, I wandered the mortal world,

11:52.630 --> 11:53.580
punishing the wicked.

11:54.360 --> 11:55.130
And before I knew it,

11:55.150 --> 11:56.620
I had earned myself a new fearsome name.

11:58.360 --> 12:00.140
No wonder people say

12:00.270 --> 12:01.910
you returned to worldly life, fell into demonhood,

12:02.240 --> 12:03.790
and became the demon monk

12:04.290 --> 12:05.610
known as Xie Lingxi.

12:07.150 --> 12:08.180
I was a demon to begin with.

12:08.960 --> 12:10.010
How could I "fall into demonhood"?

12:10.870 --> 12:12.130
I had no name in the first place.

12:12.720 --> 12:14.060
It makes little difference

12:15.550 --> 12:16.300
what the world calls me.

12:17.600 --> 12:18.980
But why did you come back here?

12:19.960 --> 12:21.700
Why do you refuse to help Wu Zhiqi

12:22.030 --> 12:23.770
lift the Petrification Curse from the Green Ape clan?

12:25.360 --> 12:26.460
You're tormenting him

12:28.360 --> 12:29.420
to take revenge on him, aren't you?

12:34.910 --> 12:36.700
I've never resented him.

12:38.550 --> 12:39.420
Why would I want revenge?

12:42.080 --> 12:42.700
I came back

12:43.670 --> 12:45.730
because of a promise I once made to Chi Wen.

12:47.240 --> 12:47.850
I promised him

12:51.320 --> 12:52.730
I would protect someone for him.

12:59.030 --> 12:59.580
So

13:02.960 --> 13:04.060
I've hated the wrong person all along.

13:05.390 --> 13:06.610
The slaughter of the flood dragon clan

13:07.670 --> 13:09.100
wasn't Shilin Sect or Chi Wen's doing...

13:31.440 --> 13:32.100
Iced lotus seeds?

13:33.600 --> 13:34.700
You can use demon magic again?

13:37.270 --> 13:38.650
I made them in my room

13:38.960 --> 13:39.900
after the prayer ceremony.

13:41.420 --> 13:42.480
When I was little,

13:43.000 --> 13:44.620
Wangyan used to make them for me all the time.

13:45.040 --> 13:46.160
They're crisp and refreshing.

13:49.960 --> 13:50.810
It feels

13:53.120 --> 13:54.530
like I've been apart from Wangyan forever.

13:59.240 --> 14:00.040
Go on. Try them.

14:00.670 --> 14:01.420
Once you've finished,

14:01.510 --> 14:02.700
we'll go get the Star Stone

14:03.030 --> 14:03.890
and get out of here.

14:11.630 --> 14:12.340
I forgot.

14:13.240 --> 14:14.220
Master Chi Wen

14:14.600 --> 14:16.250
never eats what others give him.

14:18.390 --> 14:19.340
I shouldn't have bothered...

14:39.000 --> 14:40.610
Sometimes I think

14:41.550 --> 14:43.460
about the real Di Zhu from over 1,000 years ago.

14:47.120 --> 14:47.730
Do you think

14:49.390 --> 14:50.490
she was foolish?

14:53.240 --> 14:55.820
People often say that love is a gamble,

14:56.600 --> 14:57.530
and that the heart is the stake.

15:00.600 --> 15:01.420
But some people

15:02.390 --> 15:03.990
will wager everything they have

15:05.030 --> 15:06.300
even when they're battered and bruised.

15:09.720 --> 15:11.060
But Di Zhu lost that gamble.

15:11.840 --> 15:12.980
In the legend, Man Man

15:13.240 --> 15:14.300
was a killer.

15:16.000 --> 15:16.940
But I think

15:18.120 --> 15:18.650
Man Man

15:19.390 --> 15:20.940
truly loved Di Zhu.

15:24.360 --> 15:25.700
Whether he did or not,

15:26.870 --> 15:28.460
Man Man still deceived Di Zhu.

15:30.670 --> 15:31.650
And I

15:33.240 --> 15:34.300
hate deception more than anything.

15:37.960 --> 15:40.370
Are you implying something?

15:51.850 --> 15:52.470
You...

16:30.150 --> 16:31.670
In the end, I still can't

16:32.670 --> 16:34.730
leave this Star Stone illusion, can I?

16:36.550 --> 16:37.530
A Star Stone illusion?

16:40.960 --> 16:41.820
You mean

16:43.550 --> 16:45.180
this is an illusion created by me?

16:53.670 --> 16:54.530
I understand now.

16:57.360 --> 16:58.250
In this illusion,

16:59.270 --> 17:01.300
there is a truth that you don't want him to know.

17:02.030 --> 17:03.710
So you want to kill the Star Stone

17:04.750 --> 17:06.140
and see whether that can break the illusion.

17:06.290 --> 17:08.920
My hands are already stained with blood.

17:11.310 --> 17:13.210
A little more won't matter.

17:17.480 --> 17:18.380
My weak point

17:19.350 --> 17:21.380
lies one cun below my left collarbone.

17:24.030 --> 17:24.420
Go on.

17:25.310 --> 17:26.000
Strike here.

17:31.150 --> 17:32.160
Why?

17:34.640 --> 17:35.250
Child,

17:36.400 --> 17:37.570
the shackles in your heart

17:39.070 --> 17:40.900
were not forged from your sins.

17:42.510 --> 17:43.330
Your heart

17:44.200 --> 17:46.220
has lost its way under pressure and self-torment.

17:47.270 --> 17:48.980
That's why I cannot see your heart.

17:50.480 --> 17:52.140
I'm willing to help free you from this sea of suffering.

17:53.750 --> 17:55.110
The splendor in a dream

17:56.400 --> 17:57.460
is, after all, illusory.

17:59.100 --> 18:01.900
♪You say don't look back♪

18:02.380 --> 18:04.660
♪Don't become like me♪

18:05.020 --> 18:06.940
♪Sands in the snow...♪

18:08.480 --> 18:09.490
Only when the dream ends

18:11.070 --> 18:12.180
does the truth appear.

18:15.640 --> 18:16.810
But the truth

18:18.440 --> 18:19.600
is too bitter.

18:26.400 --> 18:28.560
For the past millennium, I've been asking myself

18:30.750 --> 18:31.490
why

18:31.510 --> 18:33.070
I came into this world

18:35.180 --> 18:36.090
and what

18:38.400 --> 18:40.110
I could do for it.

18:55.550 --> 18:56.750
Master Chi Wen,

18:57.200 --> 18:58.170
you're finally awake.

18:59.570 --> 19:01.020
You were so well-behaved

19:01.350 --> 19:02.800
while you were asleep.

19:09.070 --> 19:10.940
You poisoned the iced lotus seeds?

19:12.880 --> 19:14.250
Don't make it sound so bad.

19:14.310 --> 19:15.400
It was only a sleeping draught.

19:16.350 --> 19:17.050
Still,

19:18.200 --> 19:20.460
getting you to lower your guard

19:20.920 --> 19:22.700
and obediently eat food from someone else

19:22.920 --> 19:24.180
was truly difficult.

19:24.510 --> 19:26.050
A fox really can't be trusted.

19:27.510 --> 19:28.620
What exactly are you trying to do?

19:31.270 --> 19:33.350
How can you sound so self-righteous

19:33.820 --> 19:35.540
when you were the one who played tricks first?

19:37.110 --> 19:37.710
Tell me.

19:38.510 --> 19:40.460
Why did you pour out the realgar powder from my sachet?

19:40.880 --> 19:42.380
Why are you dawdling? Come in.

19:43.290 --> 19:44.200
I'm coming.

19:55.000 --> 19:56.090
Are you that reluctant to leave?

19:58.270 --> 19:59.050
Don't tell me

19:59.720 --> 20:01.700
you really want to stay and marry me.

20:02.790 --> 20:03.960
Don't flatter yourself.

20:05.510 --> 20:07.050
I just want to catch the killer.

20:09.350 --> 20:10.570
Then I'm even more baffled.

20:11.400 --> 20:12.470
What's the point?

20:13.400 --> 20:15.010
This is an illusion of the past.

20:15.240 --> 20:16.620
None of this has anything to do with us.

20:17.400 --> 20:18.510
What happened in the past

20:18.640 --> 20:19.480
can't be undone

20:19.640 --> 20:20.410
or changed.

20:21.070 --> 20:22.420
So why go to all this extra trouble?

20:23.000 --> 20:24.420
Don't you think it's suspicious?

20:25.070 --> 20:26.220
A demon that can possess people

20:26.350 --> 20:27.620
and control them at will

20:28.240 --> 20:29.090
has always been

20:29.350 --> 20:30.220
exceedingly rare.

20:31.350 --> 20:31.940
Doesn't that

20:32.510 --> 20:33.700
remind you of anyone?

20:37.830 --> 20:38.660
Jiu Ying?

20:47.110 --> 20:48.730
You know the Star Stone better than anyone.

20:49.640 --> 20:50.940
Do the illusions inside it

20:51.480 --> 20:52.290
belong to anyone?

20:53.440 --> 20:54.420
Like dreams,

20:55.110 --> 20:56.710
whose memories are these illusions of the past

20:57.480 --> 20:58.550
they've entered?

20:59.960 --> 21:02.490
Among those who've entered the same illusion,

21:02.880 --> 21:04.290
one of them is

21:04.750 --> 21:06.150
the master of that illusion.

21:07.310 --> 21:09.140
It is a past they once lived through.

21:10.880 --> 21:12.380
But the wonder of the Star Stone

21:13.790 --> 21:15.220
is that the master's consciousness

21:16.310 --> 21:18.010
enters someone else's body

21:19.750 --> 21:21.330
to relive it all

21:23.000 --> 21:24.490
as an observer.

21:25.960 --> 21:26.460
That way,

21:27.240 --> 21:28.620
the things

21:28.720 --> 21:30.260
that have confused them for years

21:30.590 --> 21:32.950
can finally make sense when seen

21:33.440 --> 21:34.330
through an outsider's eyes.

21:35.270 --> 21:36.420
Take Wu Shiguang.

21:36.680 --> 21:37.740
He travelled

21:38.240 --> 21:40.660
to his own childhood.

21:41.400 --> 21:42.380
But he's

21:42.400 --> 21:43.510
reliving it

21:44.240 --> 21:45.660
through his father Cang Hao's perspective.

21:46.640 --> 21:47.930
So Wu Shiguang wants to find

21:48.830 --> 21:50.900
the truth behind the destruction of the flood dragon clan?

21:51.310 --> 21:51.700
No.

21:52.920 --> 21:55.110
It's the Star Stone that wants them to know the answers.

21:56.000 --> 21:56.860
The Star Stone?

21:57.110 --> 21:58.490
Didn't you see it too?

21:59.480 --> 22:00.570
It's Xie Lingxi.

22:01.720 --> 22:02.530
But

22:02.830 --> 22:04.180
the world Master Chi Wen

22:04.200 --> 22:05.010
and Lu Wuyi entered

22:05.030 --> 22:06.310
was from 1,000 years ago.

22:07.040 --> 22:08.900
It has nothing to do with either of them.

22:10.030 --> 22:11.570
Who is the master

22:13.790 --> 22:14.530
of that illusion?

22:16.350 --> 22:16.940
Bai Ze,

22:19.070 --> 22:20.380
why don't you ask me

22:21.680 --> 22:23.220
who the master is

22:23.960 --> 22:24.980
in Li Jie's illusion?

22:26.720 --> 22:27.730
So you do know.

22:29.200 --> 22:31.730
Who would've thought that Master Bai Ze, who knows everything under heaven,

22:33.110 --> 22:33.940
would have secrets too?

22:35.020 --> 22:36.310
Yuan Wuhuo.

22:38.000 --> 22:39.190
Yuan Xizai.

22:43.640 --> 22:44.490
How interesting.

22:48.310 --> 22:49.920
How did you find out where the Star Stone was hidden?

22:51.350 --> 22:53.370
Are there any other spies among the Green Ape clan?

22:54.420 --> 22:55.120
Report!

22:56.350 --> 22:57.170
Master Wu Zhiqi,

22:57.400 --> 22:58.550
Master Six-Eyed Butterfly has arrived.

22:58.680 --> 22:59.500
He's here to take the Star Stone.

23:00.030 --> 23:00.530
All right.

23:03.880 --> 23:05.980
This cage, like the chains on Tian Di,

23:06.920 --> 23:08.620
is made of tough spirit sand.

23:09.440 --> 23:11.090
Only the hardest obsidian

23:11.110 --> 23:11.900
can break it.

23:17.270 --> 23:18.140
You can't escape.

23:19.960 --> 23:20.940
And don't even think

23:21.720 --> 23:22.810
about taking Tian Di with you.

23:33.560 --> 23:34.540
You really shouldn't

23:34.560 --> 23:35.650
be trapped here by me.

23:37.640 --> 23:38.570
The world is vast,

23:40.160 --> 23:40.980
but it is cruel too.

23:42.840 --> 23:43.860
You can resent me

23:44.750 --> 23:45.610
or hate me,

23:47.070 --> 23:48.660
but some roads

23:52.720 --> 23:53.980
were destined for you and me all along.

24:16.310 --> 24:16.980
Don't be sad.

24:18.550 --> 24:19.620
He wants to let you go.

24:21.510 --> 24:22.420
Fortunately, the birthday gift

24:22.440 --> 24:23.620
my little brother gave me years ago

24:25.070 --> 24:26.290
was obsidian.

24:30.240 --> 24:32.290
Only the hardest obsidian

24:33.440 --> 24:34.290
can break it.

24:35.350 --> 24:36.330
Wu Zhiqi was

24:38.000 --> 24:39.860
reminding us on purpose.

25:07.270 --> 25:08.140
Good for you, Man Man.

25:09.270 --> 25:10.620
You knew where the Star Stone was

25:11.110 --> 25:12.090
and didn't tell me?

25:12.680 --> 25:14.180
The Star Stone isn't yours.

25:14.510 --> 25:15.460
Why should he tell you?

25:16.590 --> 25:18.010
You look human enough.

25:18.790 --> 25:19.490
Have you no shame?

25:21.270 --> 25:23.250
I knew something was off with you.

25:24.510 --> 25:25.660
Turns out you really did betray me.

25:26.440 --> 25:28.330
This woman is clearly pure trouble.

25:29.240 --> 25:30.180
A vixen through and through.

25:32.160 --> 25:33.220
Then do you know

25:34.000 --> 25:35.900
that foxes never forget a grudge?

25:36.880 --> 25:38.140
I still haven't settled the score

25:38.310 --> 25:39.420
for you killing me.

25:40.510 --> 25:41.290
Killing you?

25:42.200 --> 25:43.220
What do you mean, killing you?

25:44.030 --> 25:45.530
I'll kill you now!

26:12.440 --> 26:12.900
You...

26:15.200 --> 26:16.330
You're only human.

26:17.510 --> 26:18.850
Why are you immune to my magic?

26:25.590 --> 26:26.690
Looks like Lu Wuyi

26:26.690 --> 26:28.670
is even more formidable than we thought.

26:28.850 --> 26:29.640
Bai Ze,

26:30.240 --> 26:31.530
you know the secrets of all demons.

26:33.200 --> 26:34.700
What kind of power is this?

26:35.640 --> 26:37.030
The more she's attacked

26:37.030 --> 26:37.960
by the same kind of magic,

26:38.440 --> 26:39.250
the more she's able

26:39.310 --> 26:40.940
to absorb its power and grow immune to it.

26:50.110 --> 26:52.010
I've been away from the world too long.

26:53.030 --> 26:54.010
When did the people

26:54.510 --> 26:55.940
of the Formless Moon become this powerful?

26:57.920 --> 26:58.460
Be careful.

26:58.720 --> 26:59.660
What are you scared of?

27:01.940 --> 27:03.380
You killed me last time.

27:04.300 --> 27:07.130
Now it's time you paid back that life.

27:08.040 --> 27:09.210
What nonsense.

27:10.470 --> 27:11.780
I have no idea what you're talking about.

27:14.070 --> 27:15.050
Hand over the Star Stone.

27:15.240 --> 27:15.770
Don't act rashly.

27:16.350 --> 27:17.420
Give me the Star Stone,

27:18.510 --> 27:20.270
or I'll kill her right now.

27:20.270 --> 27:21.560
I was telling her not to act rashly.

27:25.720 --> 27:27.090
Kneel and obey me.

27:34.000 --> 27:35.250
Don't kill him. The illusion will go haywire!

28:16.020 --> 28:20.460
[The day of the Hurricane Catastrophe]

28:21.400 --> 28:22.490
I'll cut his chains.

28:22.750 --> 28:23.860
You go outside the cave first

28:24.350 --> 28:25.290
and see if there are any Green Ape guards.

28:25.750 --> 28:26.180
All right.

29:25.540 --> 29:27.540
[An hour before the Meteor Blast]

29:29.460 --> 29:31.180
A moth will fly

29:31.750 --> 29:33.060
into the flame

29:33.750 --> 29:35.310
even knowing it's wrong.

29:36.270 --> 29:36.980
I

29:38.110 --> 29:39.570
am no different.

29:56.270 --> 29:56.810
Master!

30:01.550 --> 30:02.090
Why?

30:09.070 --> 30:10.380
All things flourish and fade in their time.

30:11.720 --> 30:13.350
Life and death are nothing strange.

30:18.070 --> 30:19.490
I had hoped to see you through this,

30:21.070 --> 30:22.050
but it seems...

30:31.030 --> 30:31.750
Master...

30:33.030 --> 30:33.610
Master!

31:04.740 --> 31:10.300
[The day of the Great Freeze]

31:14.660 --> 31:16.060
What happened?

31:18.550 --> 31:20.250
The illusion seems to be jumping on its own.

31:21.830 --> 31:23.010
It's correcting itself automatically.

31:31.270 --> 31:32.770
Move that one over there.

31:32.880 --> 31:34.380
Time's jumped that far ahead?

31:46.350 --> 31:47.010
Di Zhu,

31:47.830 --> 31:48.960
here's the Star Stone!

31:52.750 --> 31:53.490
That's easy.

32:05.390 --> 32:06.650
What's going on?

32:09.040 --> 32:10.340
How did everything suddenly change?

32:13.280 --> 32:14.080
I don't know either.

32:21.720 --> 32:22.860
You're finally here.

32:31.110 --> 32:32.050
You've done well

32:32.400 --> 32:33.380
with the task we assigned you.

32:33.960 --> 32:34.570
Hand him over.

32:34.750 --> 32:35.700
I'll take him back to the Shilin Sect.

32:39.000 --> 32:40.620
The Shilin Sect will take good care of you.

32:41.550 --> 32:42.620
I'll go see you later.

32:53.350 --> 32:54.010
What are you doing?

32:55.240 --> 32:56.620
There's something hidden inside you.

32:57.270 --> 32:58.140
I'll help you take it out.

33:11.190 --> 33:13.390
Wu Shiguang is in my hands now.

33:15.640 --> 33:16.490
So it really was him.

33:21.720 --> 33:23.220
If you want him safe,

33:24.220 --> 33:26.630
lift the Petrification Curse from my clansmen.

33:34.820 --> 33:35.850
Master...

33:51.350 --> 33:52.810
Shiguang always calls you Master,

33:54.400 --> 33:55.380
but in his heart,

34:01.350 --> 34:02.980
he's always seen you as family.

34:06.160 --> 34:07.180
You're no child anymore.

34:08.800 --> 34:10.380
Why are you suddenly crying

34:10.400 --> 34:11.130
like one?

34:12.740 --> 34:13.300
♪So...♪

34:14.230 --> 34:14.820
Don't worry.

34:16.400 --> 34:17.690
I'll get Shiguang out.

34:20.740 --> 34:26.660
♪You are spring rain, your breeze drifting into my heart♪

34:27.820 --> 34:33.740
♪You are a rising tide, bringing a melody of highs and lows♪

34:34.820 --> 34:41.020
♪All my troubles are forgotten here♪

34:41.540 --> 34:47.860
♪Only you and I remain in our tiny world♪

34:49.020 --> 34:54.860
♪If you're a little boat, I'll be the shore♪

34:56.020 --> 35:02.020
♪Holding your weariness and all your joys and sorrows♪

35:03.060 --> 35:09.100
♪I truly cherish the sweetness in your smile♪

35:09.700 --> 35:15.620
♪So don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

35:17.260 --> 35:23.180
♪If you're the moon, I'll be falling snow♪

35:24.340 --> 35:31.020
♪Let them chase the skies, I'll stay with you below♪

35:31.340 --> 35:37.180
♪I truly miss the taste of your tears♪

35:37.420 --> 35:38.060
♪So please♪

35:38.380 --> 35:44.380
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

35:44.580 --> 35:45.180
♪So please♪

35:45.460 --> 35:51.060
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

35:51.660 --> 35:52.300
♪So please♪

35:52.500 --> 36:02.340
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

36:08.480 --> 36:10.260
So Master went to save me.

36:12.030 --> 36:12.830
If he hadn't gone

36:12.830 --> 36:14.780
with Wu Zhiqi that day,

36:17.230 --> 36:18.460
would everything have been different?

36:24.920 --> 36:25.530
Today

36:28.110 --> 36:29.490
is the day the flood dragon clan

36:31.510 --> 36:32.810
is wiped out.

36:47.150 --> 36:49.090
They're getting married!

36:50.030 --> 36:51.340
They're getting married!

36:53.360 --> 36:54.050
They're getting married!

36:55.800 --> 36:57.010
They're getting married!

37:03.280 --> 37:04.090
So this isn't a dream.

37:04.800 --> 37:06.240
Why didn't you pinch yourself?

37:06.590 --> 37:07.820
Because I'm not stupid.

37:07.900 --> 37:08.380
I...

37:10.670 --> 37:11.420
You know,

37:11.840 --> 37:13.980
that wedding robe looks good

37:14.400 --> 37:15.780
on you, Master Dragon Deity.

37:20.030 --> 37:20.900
A true dragon

37:21.280 --> 37:22.210
looks good in anything.

37:22.800 --> 37:23.490
No need to be surprised.

37:27.470 --> 37:29.820
A Dragon Deity above mortal concerns

37:30.360 --> 37:31.940
is suddenly decked out in gold and silver,

37:32.150 --> 37:33.170
about to wed.

37:33.510 --> 37:34.580
How's that not surprising?

37:39.000 --> 37:40.740
By the way, Master Dragon Deity,

37:41.440 --> 37:43.050
do you have any experience

37:43.510 --> 37:44.380
with the wedding night?

37:46.440 --> 37:48.010
Nothing unexpected will happen, right?

37:53.190 --> 37:53.650
Wait for me.

37:54.960 --> 37:55.510
Just wait here.

38:08.030 --> 38:10.380
I'm not getting jilted, am I?

38:29.710 --> 38:30.460
What is it?

38:32.630 --> 38:33.260
Something good.

38:57.420 --> 38:58.530
Trust me.

38:59.800 --> 39:01.780
This guarantees nothing can go wrong.

39:09.110 --> 39:09.900
Why are you smiling?

39:11.110 --> 39:11.900
You smiled first.

39:12.590 --> 39:13.210
No, you smiled first.

39:13.550 --> 39:14.260
You did first.

39:14.690 --> 39:15.670
You did first.

39:19.030 --> 39:19.530
I did first.

39:34.230 --> 39:35.820
If you make me fall, you're dead.

39:48.280 --> 39:49.980
By Sacred Heaven above,

39:50.480 --> 39:52.770
first bow to heaven and earth!

40:01.110 --> 40:02.300
- With the ancestors as witness... - Wonderful!

40:02.880 --> 40:04.050
Second bow to your kin!

40:13.190 --> 40:14.820
Let the holy mountain bear witness

40:15.230 --> 40:16.980
and the sacred waters seal your vow.

40:17.480 --> 40:19.380
Third bow to each other!

40:28.070 --> 40:28.820
I'm fine.

40:30.960 --> 40:32.820
Ceremony complete.

40:33.150 --> 40:33.900
Now kiss!

40:52.260 --> 40:55.820
♪If there's a little village down the road♪

40:56.420 --> 40:58.620
♪By a river bending soft and slow♪

40:59.060 --> 41:04.260
♪You hum a tune by the fire's glow♪

41:04.940 --> 41:08.300
♪Time would linger, never go♪

41:08.540 --> 41:13.580
♪Even the wind would fade, just you and me♪

41:13.780 --> 41:16.940
♪Hand in hand, we'd sit close, quietly♪

41:32.400 --> 41:32.900
Di Zhu,

41:34.480 --> 41:35.380
here's the Star Stone.

41:39.590 --> 41:40.380
Come out, Little Nine.

42:02.320 --> 42:02.820
Hold your breath.

42:03.440 --> 42:04.260
There's sleeping powder in the sandstorm.

42:46.960 --> 42:47.900
The Star Stone.

42:57.580 --> 42:58.740
♪It's your light♪

42:58.940 --> 43:00.820
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:00.980 --> 43:04.100
♪That set the night alight♪

43:04.460 --> 43:10.980
♪And lead me through the fight♪

43:12.740 --> 43:14.620
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

43:15.060 --> 43:19.500
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

43:20.300 --> 43:21.980
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

43:22.140 --> 43:27.540
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

43:28.300 --> 43:33.700
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

43:36.020 --> 43:42.060
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

43:43.020 --> 43:45.180
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

43:45.460 --> 43:50.300
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

43:50.660 --> 43:52.980
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

43:53.180 --> 43:58.260
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

43:58.500 --> 44:00.500
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

44:00.780 --> 44:05.140
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

44:06.140 --> 44:13.100
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

44:29.660 --> 44:32.620
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

44:33.700 --> 44:37.100
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

44:37.900 --> 44:40.420
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

44:40.660 --> 44:43.740
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

44:44.140 --> 44:46.460
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

44:46.980 --> 44:51.380
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

44:51.620 --> 44:53.780
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

44:54.180 --> 44:59.140
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

44:59.380 --> 45:00.540
♪It's your light♪

45:00.740 --> 45:02.580
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

45:02.780 --> 45:05.900
♪That set the night alight♪

45:06.660 --> 45:16.100
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
